WEBVTT

00:09:59.131 --> 00:10:01.155
While wrestling over the next few years,

00:10:01.179 --> 00:10:03.085
I suffered a pretty bad shoulder injury

00:10:03.109 --> 00:10:05.478
right around the same time
my wife and I found out

00:10:05.502 --> 00:10:07.403
that we were expecting our first child.

00:10:07.427 --> 00:10:08.770
I know what you're thinking,

00:10:08.794 --> 00:10:12.068
but believe me when I say
those two events are completely unrelated.

00:10:12.092 --> 00:10:15.334
(Laughter)

00:10:18.168 --> 00:10:21.272
But I needed shoulder surgery,

00:10:21.296 --> 00:10:23.232
and I wanted to be home with my family.

00:10:23.763 --> 00:10:25.276
It was my turn to be a dad.

00:10:26.383 --> 00:10:29.538
So on July 27, 2007,

00:10:29.562 --> 00:10:31.480
I wrestled my final match,